text: Umar Arteh Ghalib or Omer Carte Qalib (, ) (1930 - 18 November 2020) was a Somali politician. He was Prime Minister of Somalia from January 24, 1991 to May 1993.Somalia at WorldStatesmen.org Ghalib died on 18 November 2020 at the age of 90. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Prime ministers of Somalia
